      <byline class="print_byline">By STUART ELLIOT</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Primus Telecommunications Group names DeVito/Verdi as ad agency for its Primus Design Internet Services unit (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Primus Telecommunications Group, McLean, Va., to DeVito/Verdi, New York, as the first agency to handle its Primus Design Internet Services unit. Billings were estimated at $10 million.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
